    "In parallel, a high-resolution RF-AE was proposed for change point detection (CPD) in estimated RV trajectories.",
    "A control block diagram for the parallel pipeline can be found in Figure 1.",
    "This tiered approach, including the AE anomaly detection and state estimation module energy analysis, along with a system-level integration and validation approach using a mixed effects model (MEM), provides a framework for enhanced nutrient management sustainability in a range of operating environments.",
